The Hargreaves (UK) Services Limited gender pay gap, 5th April 2017 was 32.0%. 
 

This is the difference in mean (average) hourly rate between men and women. Within Hargreaves (UK) 
Services Limited there are three main areas: Logistic Services, Coal Production and Distribution and 
Plant Operations. The majority of the roles within these three sectors are shift work and irregular 
working patterns which are predominately occupied by men.  The median gender pay gap was 16.2%. 

 

