The Hargreaves Industrial Services Limited gender pay gap, 5th April 2017 was 2.2%. 
 

Hargreaves Industrial Services Limited provides a range of industrial site services to the power 
generation, steel and other industrial sectors. The services engaged in are varied and include material 
handling and operations and maintenance. The company is predominantly male due to the transient 
nature of the works however, the business has a large regional head office that has a number of 
females in senior roles hence the low gender pay gap. The median gender pay gap was 12.3%. 

 

 

